<plot>Kendra, a retired aristocrat, is shocked to find a package on her doorstep containing a collection of her credit card receipts along with a letter describing how she can obtain more information. Frustrated that someone had stolen her identity and curious to discover who's responsible, she follows the clues. In the course of her wild goose chase she visits a series of locations that she would never have otherwise seen. Forced to ask for help from the employees at each location to get the next clue, her arrogance and classist nature take over. At the last stop she's given the chance to come face to face with the perpetrator, only to discover that her preconceptions are at fault.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343484</url></doc>
